dotnetType.name: IBinaryDeserializerBuilderCase
dotnetType.summary:
Builds Avro deserializers for specific type-schema combinations. Used by
            <see cref="T:Chr.Avro.Serialization.BinaryDeserializerBuilder" /> to break apart deserializer building logic.

returns.summary:
A function that accepts a <see cref="T:System.IO.Stream" /> and returns a deserialized object. Since
            this is not a typed method, the general <see cref="T:System.Delegate" /> type is used.

overloads.summary: Builds a deserializer for a type-schema pair.
Determines whether the case can be applied to a schema.
Determines whether the case can be applied to a type resolution.
